snippet.textDisplay:
Speechless. 10:28 minutes of heaven. It has been 5 days and this goose-bump inducing magic is on the loop. Tears rolled down because of the power of the lyrics and the rendition. For people unacquainted with Urdu, who knows, while in process of understanding the meaning of lyrics, you may began a journey within.
Rohil Hyatt, Atif Aslam and entire team of Coke Studio Pakistan, take a bow. A perfect tribute to the legends, Sabri brothers. I can't forget the original qawwali at all. Now this rendition takes the spirituality to a contemporary dimension. Love from India!
snippet.textOriginal:
